<xsl:stylesheet version="2.0"
    xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform"
    xmlns:xs="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
  <xsl:decimal-format name="d" decimal-separator="," grouping-separator="."/>
  <xsl:template match="/">
    <output>

        <xsl:variable name="export"> 
            <EXPORT_JSON>
                <initAction>
                    <_type>OpenEditor</_type>
                    <tableName>9:2</tableName>
                    <editAction>DONE</editAction>
                </initAction>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>barmex</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <xsl:value-of select="concat(/ObjectNode/result/productionOrder/externalId, /ObjectNode/result/name)" />
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>gutmge</fieldName>
                    <value>            
                        <xsl:value-of select="number(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/productionNumbers[last()]/acceptedMeasurement/amount)" />
                    </value>
                    <rowSpec>
                        <xsl:value-of select="concat('$,artikel=', /ObjectNode/result/productionOrder/product/name)" />
                    </rowSpec>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>bzeit</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <!--<xsl:value-of select="format-number((xs:dateTime(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/endDateTime) - xs:dateTime(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[1]/startDateTime)) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1H') , '#.###,00', 'd')" />-->
                        <xsl:variable name="rawSeconds" select="xs:double(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeDurations/work)"/>
                        <xsl:variable name="work_seconds">
                            <xsl:choose>
                                    <xsl:when test="string($rawSeconds) = '' or not(xs:double($rawSeconds))">
                                        <!-- Set $seconds to 0 when empty or erroneous -->
                                        <xsl:value-of select="0"/>
                                    </xsl:when>
                                    <xsl:otherwise>
                                        <!-- Otherwise, set $seconds to the parsed double value -->
                                        <xsl:value-of select="format-number($rawSeconds, '#.##')"/>
                                    </xsl:otherwise>
                                </xsl:choose> 
                        </xsl:variable>
                        
                        <xsl:value-of select="format-number(xs:dayTimeDuration(concat('PT', $work_seconds, 'S')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1H') , '#.###,00', 'd')" />
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>mzeit</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <!--<xsl:value-of select="format-number((xs:dateTime(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/endDateTime) - xs:dateTime(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[1]/startDateTime)) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1H') , '#.###,00', 'd')" />-->
                        <xsl:variable name="rawSeconds" select="xs:double(/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeDurations/work)"/>
                        <xsl:variable name="work_seconds">
                            <xsl:choose>
                                    <xsl:when test="string($rawSeconds) = '' or not(xs:double($rawSeconds))">
                                        <!-- Set $seconds to 0 when empty or erroneous -->
                                        <xsl:value-of select="0"/>
                                    </xsl:when>
                                    <xsl:otherwise>
                                        <!-- Otherwise, set $seconds to the parsed double value -->
                                        <xsl:value-of select="format-number($rawSeconds, '#.##')"/>
                                    </xsl:otherwise>
                                </xsl:choose> 
                        </xsl:variable>
                        
                        <xsl:value-of select="format-number(xs:dayTimeDuration(concat('PT', $work_seconds, 'S')) div xs:dayTimeDuration('PT1H') , '#.###,00', 'd')" />
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>ma</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/responseUser/externalId" />
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>rzbuchen</fieldName>
                    <value>true</value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>yerfzeit</fieldName>
                    <value>
                    <xsl:value-of select="format-dateTime(current-dateTime(),'[D01].[M01].[Y0001]_[H01]:[m01]')"/>
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>yerfdat</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <xsl:value-of select="format-dateTime(current-dateTime(),'[Y0001][M01][D01]')"/>
                    </value>
                </actions>
                <actions>
                    <_type>SetFieldValue</_type>
                    <fieldName>bem</fieldName>
                    <value>
                        <xsl:value-of select="concat(format-dateTime(current-dateTime(),'[D01].[M01].[Y0001]'), ' ', /ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/responseUser/externalId, ' ', /ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/responseUser/userName, ';BDE')" />
                    </value>
                </actions>
            </EXPORT_JSON>        
        </xsl:variable>

        <bookingEntry>
            <machineOccupation>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/externalId"/>
                </externalId>
            </machineOccupation>            
            <subProductionStep>
                <externalId>
                    <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/externalId"/>
                </externalId>
            </subProductionStep>
            <isStepTime>true</isStepTime>
            <bookingState>NEW</bookingState>
            <xsl:if test="/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/responseUser/externalId != ''">
                <user>
                    <externalId>
                        <xsl:value-of select="/ObjectNode/result/subProductionSteps[id = /ObjectNode/additional]/timeRecords[last()]/responseUser/externalId"/>
                    </externalId>
                </user>
            </xsl:if>                       
            <message>
                <xsl:copy-of select="$export"/>
            </message>
        </bookingEntry> 

    </output>
  </xsl:template>
</xsl:stylesheet>
